        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I think this would be a nice improvement if people were able to cast variables from {{Zend_Controller_Abstract::getParam()}}, etc..\n\nWhat I mean is, for example (inside a controller):\n\n{code}\n$id = $this->_request->getParam('id', null, Zend_Controller::INT);\nif ($id === null) {\n\/\/ do something else\n}\necho $id; \/\/ it's an integer, WOOHOO.\n{code}\n\nI'd propose to have at least:\n- integer ({{Zend_Controller::INT}})\n- float ({{Zend_Controller::FLOAT}})\n- string ({{Zend_Controller::STRING}})\n- boolean ({{Zend_Controller::BOOL}})"
        },
